For too long, our communities, and especially communities of color, have been unjustly harmed by outdated laws on marijuana.

@POTUS' decision to pardon thousands for simple marijuana possession is a big first step to right this wrong.
https://t.co/p3hYLcxOZh

@USDOT must require airlines to:

✈️Advertise and sell only as many flights as they have adequate personnel to fly and support.

💰Refund passengers when flights are canceled or rescheduled and give them more money for the extra costs they incur from delays and cancelations.

Crisis pregnancy centers exist to discourage people from having an abortion and they don’t offer health care services.

Yet, when people use @google to search for access to safe abortion services, @googlemaps leads them to these centers.

@Google must fix this issue immediately.

We're forcing drug manufacturer @MNK to pay $26.8 million to New York for defrauding Medicaid.

@MNK spent years underpaying millions of Medicaid drug rebates, skirting the law for its own corporate gain.

We will protect New Yorkers from companies that cheat the system.

@sameday_testing This is the third company we have warned this week to stop misleading people about turnaround times for COVID test results.

If this has happened to you, please report it to my office:

https://t.co/CQkePbYTbh

With over 400 bills nationwide this year alone aiming to restrict the right to vote, it's no secret that the most powerful tool in our democracy is under attack.
 
@AGKarlRacine and I are fighting these efforts to protect the right to vote.⬇️
https://t.co/x78NQjH3Zi

